#. Tag: title
#: configuring.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure &kappname;"
msgstr "Konfigurirajte &kappname;"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:3
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selecting <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure "
"<replaceable>Application</replaceable>...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> from "
"the menu brings up the <guilabel>Configure</guilabel> dialog box. This "
"dialog can be used to alter a number of different settings. The settings "
"available for change vary according to which category the user chooses from "
"a vertical list on the left side of the dialog. By means of three buttons "
"along the bottom of the box the user can control the process."
msgstr ""
"Če v meniju izberete <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj <replaceable>Aplikacijo</replaceable>...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>, se prikaže pogovorno okno <guilabel>Konfiguriraj</"
"guilabel> škatla. To pogovorno okno lahko uporabite za spreminjanje "
"številnih različnih nastavitev. Nastavitve, ki so na voljo za spreminjanje, "
"se razlikujejo glede na to, katero kategorijo uporabnik izbere z navpičnega "
"seznama na levi strani pogovornega okna. S pomočjo treh gumbov na dnu škatle "
"lahko uporabnik nadzoruje proces."

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may invoke the <guilabel>Help</guilabel> system, accept the current "
"settings and close the dialog by means of the <guibutton>OK</guibutton> "
"button, or <guibutton>Cancel</guibutton> the process. The categories "
"<guilabel>Appearance</guilabel>, <guilabel>Fonts &amp; Colors</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Editing</guilabel>, <guilabel>Open/Save</guilabel> and "
"<guilabel>Extensions</guilabel> are detailed below."
msgstr ""
"Lahko pokličete sistem <guilabel>pomoči</guilabel>, sprejmete trenutne "
"nastavitve in zaprete pogovorno okno z gumbom <guibutton>V redu</guibutton> "
"ali <guibutton>prekličete</guibutton> postopek. Kategorije <guilabel>Videz</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Pisave &amp; Spodaj so podrobno opisane barve</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Urejanje</guilabel>, <guilabel>Odpri/Shrani</guilabel> "
"in <guilabel>Razširitve</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: configuring.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Editor Component Configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija komponente urejevalnika"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This group contains all pages related to the editor component of &kappname;. "
"Most of the settings here are defaults, they can be overridden by <link "
"linkend=\"pref-open-save-modes-filetypes\">defining a filetype</link>, by "
"<link linkend=\"config-variables\">Document Variables</link> or by changing "
"them per document during an editing session."
msgstr ""
"Ta skupina vsebuje vse strani, povezane z urejevalnikom &kappname;. Večina "
"nastavitev tukaj je privzetih in jih je mogoče preglasiti z <link linkend="
"\"pref-open-save-modes-filetypes\">definiranjem vrste datoteke</link>, s "
"<link linkend=\"config-variables\">spremenljivkami dokumenta </link> ali "
"tako, da jih spremenite za vsak dokument med sejo urejanja."

#. Tag: title
#: configuring.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid "Appearance"
msgstr "Videz"

#. Tag: title
#: configuring.docbook:34 configuring.docbook:353 configuring.docbook:786
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>General</title>"
msgstr "<title>Splošno</title>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editor font"
msgstr "Pisava urejevalnika"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can choose the font of the editor text. You can choose from any "
"font available on your system, and set a default size. A sample text is "
"displayed at the bottom of the dialog, so you can see the effect of your "
"choices."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko izberete pisavo besedila urejevalnika. Izbirate lahko med katero "
"koli pisavo, ki je na voljo v vašem sistemu, in nastavite privzeto velikost. "
"Vzorčno besedilo je prikazano na dnu pogovornega okna, tako da lahko vidite "
"učinek svojih izbir."

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information about selecting a font, see the <ulink url=\"help:/"
"fundamentals/fonts.html\"><emphasis>Choosing Fonts</emphasis> section of the "
"<emphasis>&kde; Fundamentals</emphasis> documentation</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij o izbiri pisave glejte razdelek <ulink url=\"help:/"
"fundamentals/fonts.html\"><emphasis>Izbira pisav</emphasis> v "
"<emphasis>&kde; Osnove</emphasis> dokumentacija</ulink>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show whitespace indicators"
msgstr "Pokaži indikatorje presledkov"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "Never"
msgstr "Nikoli"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The editor will never display dots to indicate the presence of whitespace."
msgstr ""
"Urejevalnik ne bo nikoli prikazal pik, ki bi pokazale prisotnost presledkov."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid "At the end of a line"
msgstr "Na koncu vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The editor will display dots to indicate the presence of extra whitespace at "
"the end of lines."
msgstr ""
"Urejevalnik bo prikazal pike, ki označujejo prisotnost dodatnega presledka "
"na koncu vrstic."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid "Always"
msgstr "Vedno"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The editor will always display dots to indicate the presence of whitespace."
msgstr ""
"Urejevalnik bo vedno prikazal pike, ki označujejo prisotnost presledkov."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "Whitespace indicator size"
msgstr "Velikost indikatorja presledka"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use the slider to change the size of the visible indicator marker."
msgstr "Z drsnikom spremenite velikost vidnega kazalnika."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show tab indicators"
msgstr "Pokaži indikatorje zavihkov"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When checked the editor will display a &raquo; symbol to indicate the "
"presence of a tab in the text."
msgstr ""
"Ko je označeno, bo urejevalnik prikazal &raquo; simbol, ki označuje "
"prisotnost zavihka v besedilu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bracket matching"
msgstr "Ujemanje oklepajev"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "Highlight range between selected brackets"
msgstr "Označi obseg med izbranimi oklepaji"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this is enabled, the range between the selected matching brackets will be "
"highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Če je to omogočeno, bo obseg med izbranimi ujemajočimi se oklepaji označen."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show preview of matching open bracket"
msgstr "Pokaži predogled ujemajočega se odprtega oklepaja"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When enabled, the editor will show a tooltip of the matching open bracket."
msgstr ""
"Ko je omogočeno, bo urejevalnik prikazal opis orodja ujemajočega se odprtega "
"oklepaja."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "Flash matching bracket when cursor moves to other bracket in pair"
msgstr ""
"Utripa ujemajoči se oklepaj, ko se kazalec premakne na drug oklepaj v paru"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If enabled, moving on the brackets (<keycap>{</keycap>, <keycap>[</keycap>, "
"<keycap>]</keycap>, <keycap>}</keycap>,<keycap>(</keycap> or <keycap>)</"
"keycap>) will quickly flash the matching bracket."
msgstr ""
"Če je omogočeno, premikanje po oklepajih (<keycap>{</keycap>, <keycap>[</"
"keycap>, <keycap>]</keycap>, <keycap>}</keycap>,<keycap>(</keycap> ali "
"<keycap>)</keycap>) bo hitro utripal ustrezni oklepaj."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show indentation lines"
msgstr "Prikaži črte zamikov"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this is checked, the editor will display vertical lines to help "
"identifying indent lines."
msgstr ""
"Če je to označeno, bo urejevalnik prikazal navpične črte za pomoč pri "
"prepoznavanju zamikov."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid "Counts"
msgstr "Šteje"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show word count"
msgstr "Pokaži število besed"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays the number of words and characters in the document and in the "
"current selection in the status bar. This option is also available in the "
"status bar context menu."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže število besed in znakov v dokumentu in v trenutnem izboru v vrstici "
"stanja. Ta možnost je na voljo tudi v kontekstnem meniju vrstice stanja."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show line count"
msgstr "Pokaži število vrstic"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays the number of total lines in the document in the status bar. This "
"option is also available in the status bar context menu."
msgstr ""
"V statusni vrstici prikaže skupno število vrstic v dokumentu. Ta možnost je "
"na voljo tudi v kontekstnem meniju vrstice stanja."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fold first line"
msgstr "Prepognite prvo vrstico"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If enabled, the first line is folded, if possible. This is useful, if the "
"file starts with a comment, such as a copyright"
msgstr ""
"Če je omogočeno, je prva vrstica prepognjena, če je to mogoče. To je "
"uporabno, če se datoteka začne s komentarjem, kot je avtorska pravica"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid "Dynamic Word Wrap"
msgstr "Dinamični prelom besed"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is checked, the text lines will be wrapped at the view border "
"on the screen."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost označena, bodo vrstice besedila obrobljene ob meji pogleda "
"na zaslonu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid "Wrap dynamically at static word wrap marker"
msgstr "Dinamično prelomi pri statičnem označevalniku preloma besed"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When checked, editor wraps lines dynamically at the <link linkend=\"pref-"
"word-wrap\">static word wrap position</link>."
msgstr ""
"Ko je označeno, urejevalnik dinamično prelomi vrstice na <link linkend="
"\"pref-word-wrap\">statični položaj preloma besed</link>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid "Disregard word boundaries for dynamic wrapping"
msgstr "Ne upoštevajte besednih meja za dinamično oblivanje"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When checked, the editor does not take into account word boundaries when "
"wrapping text lines."
msgstr ""
"Ko je označeno, urejevalnik ne upošteva besednih meja pri prelivanju "
"besedilnih vrstic."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid "Dynamic word wrap indicators"
msgstr "Indikatorji dinamičnega preloma besed"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose when the Dynamic word wrap indicators should be displayed, either "
"<guilabel>Off</guilabel>, <guilabel>Follow Line Numbers</guilabel> or "
"<guilabel>Always on</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Izberite, kdaj naj bodo indikatorji dinamičnega preloma besed prikazani, "
"<guilabel>Izklopljeno</guilabel>, <guilabel>Sledi številkam vrstic</"
"guilabel> ali <guilabel>Vedno vključeno</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:172
#, no-c-format
msgid "Indent wrapped lines"
msgstr "Zamik previtih vrstic"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally, this allows you to set a maximum width of the screen, as a "
"percentage, after which dynamically wrapped lines will no longer be "
"vertically aligned. For example, at 50%, lines whose indentation levels are "
"deeper than 50% of the width of the screen will not have vertical alignment "
"applied to subsequent wrapped lines."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega vam to omogoča nastavitev največje širine zaslona v odstotkih, po "
"kateri dinamično zavite vrstice ne bodo več navpično poravnane. Na primer, "
"pri 50 % črtah, katerih stopnja zamika je globlja od 50 % širine zaslona, ne "
"bo uporabljena navpična poravnava za naslednje previte vrstice."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid "Line Height Multiplier"
msgstr "Množitelj višine vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This value will be multiplied by the font's default line height. A value of "
"1.0 means that the default height will be used."
msgstr ""
"Ta vrednost bo pomnožena s privzeto višino vrstice pisave. Vrednost 1,0 "
"pomeni, da bo uporabljena privzeta višina."

#. Tag: title
#: configuring.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid "Borders"
msgstr "Meje"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid "Code block folding"
msgstr "Zlaganje bloka kode"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:198
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show arrows to collapse code blocks"
msgstr "Prikaži puščice za strnitev blokov kode"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is checked, the current view will display marks for code "
"folding, if code folding is available."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost označena, bo trenutni pogled prikazal oznake za zlaganje "
"kode, če je na voljo zlaganje kode."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show preview of folded blocks on hover"
msgstr "Prikaži predogled prepognjenih blokov ob lebdenju"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, hovering over a folded region shows a preview of the folded text "
"in a popup."
msgstr ""
"Če je označeno, se s kazalcem miške nad prepognjeno regijo prikaže predogled "
"prepognjenega besedila v pojavnem oknu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid "Folding arrows visibility"
msgstr "Vidnost zložljivih puščic"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Switch the folding arrows between <guimenuitem>Show on Hover</guimenuitem> "
"and <guimenuitem>Show Always</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Preklapljajte pregibne puščice med <guimenuitem>Prikaži ob lebdenju</"
"guimenuitem> in <guimenuitem>Prikaži vedno</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid "Left side"
msgstr "Leva stran"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:229 configuring.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show marks"
msgstr "Prikaži oznake"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this is checked, you will see an icon border on the left hand side. The "
"icon border shows bookmark signs for instance."
msgstr ""
"Če je to označeno, boste na levi strani videli obrobo ikone. Obroba ikone na "
"primer prikazuje znake zaznamkov."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:235
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show line numbers"
msgstr "Pokaži številke vrstic"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid "If this is checked, you will see line numbers on the left hand side."
msgstr "Če je to označeno, boste na levi strani videli številke vrstic."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid "Highlight changed and unsaved lines"
msgstr "Označite spremenjene in neshranjene vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:243
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this is checked, line modification markers will be visible. For more "
"information, see <xref linkend=\"kate-part-line-modification\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Če je to označeno, bodo vidni označevalci sprememb vrstic. Za več informacij "
"glejte <xref linkend=\"kate-part-line-modification\"/>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:254
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scrollbars"
msgstr "Drsni trakovi"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:260
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is checked the current view will show marks on the vertical "
"scrollbar. These marks will for instance show bookmarks."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost označena, bodo trenutni pogled prikazovali oznake na "
"navpičnem drsnem traku. Te oznake bodo na primer prikazale zaznamke."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show preview when hovering over scrollbar"
msgstr "Prikaži predogled, ko miškin kazalec premaknete nad drsni trak"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:266
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is checked, and you hover the scrollbar with the mouse cursor "
"a small text preview with several lines of the current document around the "
"cursor position will be displayed. This allows you to quickly switch to "
"another part of the document."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost označena in se z miškinim kazalcem pomaknete na drsni trak, "
"se prikaže majhen predogled besedila z več vrsticami trenutnega dokumenta "
"okoli položaja kazalke. To vam omogoča hiter preklop na drug del dokumenta."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:278
#, no-c-format
msgid "Minimap"
msgstr "Mini zemljevid"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show minimap"
msgstr "Pokaži mini zemljevid"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:283
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is checked, every new view will show a minimap of the "
"document on the vertical scrollbar."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost označena, bo vsak nov pogled prikazal mini zemljevid "
"dokumenta na navpičnem drsnem traku."

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:285
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information on the scrollbar minimap, see <xref linkend=\"kate-part-"
"scrollbar-minimap\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij o mini zemljevidu drsnega traku glejte <xref linkend="
"\"kate-part-scrollbar-minimap\"/>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:289
#, no-c-format
msgid "Minimap Width"
msgstr "Širina minikarte"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:290
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adjusts the width of the scrollbar mini-map, defined in pixels."
msgstr ""
"Prilagodi širino mini zemljevida drsnega traku, definiranega v slikovnih "
"pikah."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scrollbars visibility"
msgstr "Vidnost drsnih trakov"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:295
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Switch the scrollbar on, off or show the scrollbar only when needed. Click "
"with the &LMB; on the blue rectangle to display the line number range of the "
"document displayed on the screen. Keep the &LMB; pressed outside the blue "
"rectangle to automatically scroll through the document."
msgstr ""
"Vklopite, izklopite drsni trak ali ga prikažite le, ko je to potrebno. "
"Kliknite z &LMB; na modrem pravokotniku za prikaz obsega številk vrstice "
"dokumenta, prikazanega na zaslonu. Obdržite &LMB; pritisnjen zunaj modrega "
"pravokotnika za samodejno pomikanje po dokumentu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:307
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sort bookmarks menu"
msgstr "Meni Razvrsti zaznamke"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:311
#, no-c-format
msgid "By date created"
msgstr "Po datumu ustvarjanja"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:313
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each new bookmark will be added to the bottom, independently from where it "
"is placed in the document."
msgstr "Vsak nov zaznamek bo dodan na dno, ne glede na mesto v dokumentu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:317
#, no-c-format
msgid "By line number"
msgstr "Po številki vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:319
#, no-c-format
msgid "The bookmarks will be ordered by the line numbers they are placed at."
msgstr ""
"Zaznamki bodo razvrščeni po številkah vrstic, v katerih so postavljeni."

#. Tag: title
#: configuring.docbook:331
#, no-c-format
msgid "Color Themes"
msgstr "Barvne teme"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:333
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This section of the dialog lets you configure all colors in any color theme "
"you have, and create new themes, delete existing ones or just "
"<guilabel>Follow System Color Scheme</guilabel>. Each scheme has settings "
"for colors and normal and highlighted text styles."
msgstr ""
"Ta razdelek pogovornega okna vam omogoča konfiguracijo vseh barv v kateri "
"koli barvni temi, ki jo imate, in ustvarjanje novih tem, brisanje obstoječih "
"ali preprosto <guilabel>Sledite sistemski barvni shemi</guilabel>. Vsaka "
"shema ima nastavitve za barve ter običajne in poudarjene sloge besedila."

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:340
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kappname; will preselect the currently active theme for you, if you want to "
"work on a different theme start by selecting that from the <guilabel>Select "
"theme</guilabel> combobox. With the <guibutton>Copy</guibutton> and "
"<guibutton>Delete</guibutton> buttons you can create a new theme (copying an "
"existing one) or delete existing ones."
msgstr ""
"&kappname; bo namesto vas vnaprej izbral trenutno aktivno temo, če želite "
"delati na drugi temi, začnite tako, da jo izberete v kombiniranem polju "
"<guilabel>Izberi temo</guilabel>. Z gumboma <guibutton>Kopiraj</guibutton> "
"in <guibutton>Izbriši</guibutton> lahko ustvarite novo temo (kopirate "
"obstoječo) ali izbrišete obstoječe."

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid "This is described in detail in <xref linkend=\"color-themes-gui\"/>."
msgstr "To je podrobno opisano v <xref linkend=\"color-themes-gui\"/>."

#. Tag: title
#: configuring.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing"
msgstr "Urejanje"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:357
#, no-c-format
msgid "Word wrap"
msgstr "Prelom besed"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Word wrap is a feature that causes the editor to automatically start a new "
"line of text and move (wrap) the cursor to the beginning of that new line. "
"&kappname; will automatically start a new line of text when the current line "
"reaches the length specified by the <link linkend=\"pref-wrap-words-at"
"\">Wrap words at:</link> option."
msgstr ""
"Prelom besed je funkcija, ki povzroči, da urejevalnik samodejno začne novo "
"vrstico besedila in premakne (prelomi) kazalec na začetek te nove vrstice. "
"&kappname; samodejno začne novo vrstico besedila, ko trenutna vrstica doseže "
"dolžino, določeno z možnostjo <link linkend=\"pref-wrap-words-at\">Prelomi "
"besede na:</link>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:366
#, no-c-format
msgid "Wrap words at a fixed column"
msgstr "Zavijte besede v fiksni stolpec"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid "Turns static word wrap on or off."
msgstr "Vklopi ali izklopi statični prelom besed."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:372
#, no-c-format
msgid "Draw vertical line at the word wrap column"
msgstr "Narišite navpično črto v stolpcu za prelom besed"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:374
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is checked, a vertical line will be drawn at the word wrap "
"column as defined in the <menuchoice> <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Configure Editor...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in the Editing "
"tab. Please note that the word wrap marker is only drawn if you use a fixed "
"pitch font."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost označena, bo na stolpcu za prelom besed narisana navpična "
"črta, kot je definirano v <menuchoice> <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj urejevalnik ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> v "
"Zavihek za urejanje. Upoštevajte, da je oznaka za prelom besed narisana le, "
"če uporabljate pisavo s fiksno višino."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:382
#, no-c-format
msgid "Wrap words at:"
msgstr "Prelomi besede na:"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:384
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the <link linkend=\"pref-word-wrap\">Wrap words at a fixed column</link> "
"option is selected this entry determines the length (in characters) at which "
"the editor will automatically start a new line."
msgstr ""
"Če je izbrana možnost <link linkend=\"pref-word-wrap\">Prelomi besede v "
"fiksni stolpec</link>, ta vnos določa dolžino (v znakih), pri kateri bo "
"urejevalnik samodejno začel novo vrstico."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:393
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default input mode"
msgstr "Privzeti način vnosa"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:393
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The selected input mode will be enabled when opening a new view. You can "
"still toggle the vi input mode on/off for a particular view in the "
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"Izbrani način vnosa bo omogočen, ko odprete nov pogled. Še vedno lahko "
"vklopite/izklopite način vnosa vi za določen pogled v meniju <guimenu>Uredi</"
"guimenu>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:402
#, no-c-format
msgid "Brackets"
msgstr "Oklepaji"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:403
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the <guilabel>Automatically close brackets when opening bracket is typed</"
"guilabel> option is selected when the user types a left bracket (<keycap>[</"
"keycap>, <keycap>(</keycap>, or <keycap>{</keycap>) &kappname; automatically "
"enters the right bracket (<keycap>}</keycap>, <keycap>)</keycap>, or "
"<keycap>]</keycap>) to the right of the cursor."
msgstr ""
"Če je izbrana možnost <guilabel>Samodejno zapri oklepaj ob vnosu "
"odpirajočega oklepaja</guilabel>, ko uporabnik vnese levi oklepaj "
"(<keycap>[</keycap>, <keycap>(</keycap> ali <keycap> {</keycap>) &kappname; "
"samodejno vnese desni oklepaj (<keycap>}</keycap>, <keycap>)</keycap> ali "
"<keycap>]</keycap>) desno od kazalke."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:411
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enclosing characters"
msgstr "Oklepni znaki"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:412
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is possible to select the enclosing characters using the corresponding "
"drop-down list."
msgstr "S pomočjo ustreznega spustnega seznama je možno izbrati obrobne znake."

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:413
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When text is selected, typing one of these characters wraps the selected "
"text."
msgstr ""
"Ko je besedilo izbrano, vnos enega od teh znakov prelomi izbrano besedilo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:418
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy and paste"
msgstr "Kopiraj in prilepi"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:422
#, no-c-format
msgid "Move selected text when dragged"
msgstr "Premakni izbrano besedilo med vlečenjem"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:423
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option enables drag-and-drop of the selected text inside the editor "
"window."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost omogoča vlečenje in spuščanje izbranega besedila znotraj okna "
"urejevalnika."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:426
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy/cut the current line if invoked without any text selected"
msgstr ""
"Kopiraj/izreži trenutno vrstico, če je priklicana brez izbranega besedila"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:427
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is enabled and the text selection is empty, copy and cut "
"action are performed for the line of text at the actual cursor position."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost omogočena in je izbor besedila prazen, se dejanja kopiranja "
"in izrezovanja izvedejo za vrstico besedila na dejanskem položaju kazalke."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:431
#, no-c-format
msgid "Don't move the text cursor when pasting by mouse"
msgstr "Pri lepljenju z miško ne premikajte kazalca besedila"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:432
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is enabled and you paste some text in the editor window with "
"the &MMB; clicking, &kappname; will not move the text cursor into the "
"clicked position."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost omogočena in prilepite besedilo v okno urejevalnika s tipko "
"&MMB; klik, &kappname; ne bo premaknil kazalca besedila na položaj, kjer ste "
"kliknili."

#. Tag: title
#: configuring.docbook:443
#, no-c-format
msgid "Text Navigation"
msgstr "Besedilna navigacija"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:448
#, no-c-format
msgid "Text Cursor Movement"
msgstr "Premikanje kazalca besedila"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:452
#, no-c-format
msgid "Smart home and smart end"
msgstr "Pameten dom in pameten konec"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:454
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When selected, pressing the home key will cause the cursor to skip white "
"space and go to the start of a line's text."
msgstr ""
"Ko je izbrana, bo pritisk tipke Domov povzročil, da kazalec preskoči prazen "
"prostor in se premakne na začetek besedila vrstice."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:459
#, no-c-format
msgid "PageUp/PageDown moves cursor"
msgstr "PageUp/PageDown premakne kazalko"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:461
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option changes the behavior of the cursor when the user presses the "
"&PgUp; or &PgDn; key. If unselected the text cursor will maintain its "
"relative position within the visible text in &kappname; as new text becomes "
"visible as a result of the operation. So if the cursor is in the middle of "
"the visible text when the operation occurs it will remain there (except when "
"one reaches the beginning or end.) With this option selected, the first key "
"press will cause the cursor to move to either the top or bottom of the "
"visible text as a new page of text is displayed."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost spremeni obnašanje kazalca, ko uporabnik pritisne &PgUp; ali "
"&PgDn; ključ. Če ni izbran, bo besedilni kazalec ohranil svoj relativni "
"položaj znotraj vidnega besedila v &kappname; kot novo besedilo postane "
"vidno kot rezultat operacije. Torej, če je kazalec na sredini vidnega "
"besedila, ko se izvede operacija, bo ostal tam (razen ko dosežete začetek "
"ali konec.) Ko je izbrana ta možnost, bo prvi pritisk tipke povzročil, da se "
"kazalec premakne bodisi na vrh ali na dnu vidnega besedila, ko se prikaže "
"nova stran besedila."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:472
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable camel case cursor movement"
msgstr "Omogoči premikanje kazalca v kamelji obliki"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:474
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option changes the behavior of the cursor when the user presses the "
"<keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Left arrow</keycap></keycombo> or <keycombo>&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>Right arrow</keycap></keycombo> shortcut. If unselected the text "
"cursor jumps over the full words. With this option selected, the cursor "
"jumps break at camel case humps."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost spremeni vedenje kazalca, ko uporabnik pritisne <keycombo>&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>Puščico levo</keycap></keycombo> ali <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>Puščico "
"desno</keycap></keycombo> bližnjica. Če ni izbrana, kazalka besedila skoči "
"čez celotne besede. Ko je izbrana ta možnost, kazalka skoči in se prekine na "
"grbinah kamel."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:482
#, no-c-format
msgid "Autocenter cursor:"
msgstr "Kazalec samodejnega središča:"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:484
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets the number of lines to maintain visible above and below the cursor when "
"possible."
msgstr ""
"Nastavi število vrstic, ki naj ostanejo vidne nad in pod kazalcem, kadar je "
"to mogoče."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:493
#, no-c-format
msgid "Text Selection Mode"
msgstr "Način izbire besedila"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:497
#, no-c-format
msgid "Normal"
msgstr "Običajno"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:499
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selections will be overwritten by typed text and will be lost on cursor "
"movement."
msgstr ""
"Izbire bo prepisalo vtipkano besedilo in bodo izgubljeni ob premikanju "
"kazalca."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:504
#, no-c-format
msgid "Persistent"
msgstr "Vztrajen"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:506
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selections will stay even after cursor movement and typing."
msgstr "Izbire bodo ostale tudi po premikanju kazalca in tipkanju."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:510
#, no-c-format
msgid "Allow scrolling past the end of the document"
msgstr "Dovoli pomikanje čez konec dokumenta"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:511
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option lets you scroll past the end of the document. This can be used "
"to vertically centre the bottom of the document, or put it on top of the "
"current view."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost vam omogoča, da se pomaknete čez konec dokumenta. To lahko "
"uporabite za navpično centriranje dna dokumenta ali pa ga postavite na vrh "
"trenutnega pogleda."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:514
#, no-c-format
msgid "Backspace key removes character’s base with its diacritics"
msgstr "Tipka vračalka odstrani osnovo znakov z diakritičnimi znaki"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:515
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When selected, composed characters are removed with their diacritics instead "
"of only removing the base character. This is useful for Indic locales."
msgstr ""
"Ko izberete, se sestavljeni znaki odstranijo z diakritičnimi znaki, namesto "
"da se odstrani le osnovni znak. To je uporabno za indijske jezike."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:524
#, no-c-format
msgid "Multicursor modifier"
msgstr "Modifikator večkurzorja"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:526
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option lets you set the modifier that will be used to create multiple "
"cursors with &LMB; click. You need to press the modifiers and click &LMB; to "
"create a cursor at the desired location. See <link linkend=\"kate-part-"
"create-multiple-cursors\">Creating multiple cursors</link> to discover other "
"ways to create multiple cursors."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost vam omogoča nastavitev modifikatorja, ki bo uporabljen za "
"ustvarjanje več kazalcev z &LMB; kliknite. Pritisniti morate modifikatorje "
"in klikniti &LMB; ustvarite kazalec na želenem mestu. Glejte <link linkend="
"\"kate-part-create-multiple-cursors\">Ustvarjanje več kazalcev</link>, če "
"želite odkriti druge načine za ustvarjanje več kazalcev."

#. Tag: title
#: configuring.docbook:534
#, no-c-format
msgid "Indentation"
msgstr "Zamik"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:539
#, no-c-format
msgid "Default indentation mode:"
msgstr "Privzeti način zamika:"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:541
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the automatic indentation mode you want to use as default. It is "
"strongly recommended to use <userinput>None</userinput> or "
"<userinput>Normal</userinput> here, and use filetype configurations to set "
"other indentation modes for text formats like C/C++ code or &XML;."
msgstr ""
"Izberite način samodejnega zamika, ki ga želite uporabiti kot privzetega. "
"Zelo priporočljivo je, da tukaj uporabite <userinput>Brez</userinput> ali "
"<userinput>Normalno</userinput> in uporabite konfiguracije vrste datotek za "
"nastavitev drugih načinov zamika za besedilne formate, kot sta koda C/C++ "
"ali &XML;."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:549
#, no-c-format
msgid "Indent using"
msgstr "Uporaba zamika"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:553
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tabulators"
msgstr "Tabulatorji"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:555
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When this is enabled the editor will insert tabulator characters when you "
"press the &Tab; key or use <link linkend=\"kate-part-autoindent\">automatic "
"indentation</link>."
msgstr ""
"Ko je to omogočeno, bo urejevalnik vstavil tabulatorske znake, ko pritisnete "
"gumb &Tab; tipko ali uporabite <link linkend=\"kate-part-autoindent"
"\">samodejno zamikanje</link>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:561
#, no-c-format
msgid "Spaces"
msgstr "Presledki"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:563
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When this is enabled the editor will insert a calculated number of spaces "
"according to the position in the text and the <option>tab-width</option> "
"setting when you press the &Tab; key or use <link linkend=\"kate-part-"
"autoindent\">automatic indentation</link>."
msgstr ""
"Ko je to omogočeno, bo urejevalnik vstavil izračunano število presledkov "
"glede na položaj v besedilu in nastavitev <option>širine zavihka</option>, "
"ko pritisnete gumb &Tab; tipko ali uporabite <link linkend=\"kate-part-"
"autoindent\">samodejno zamikanje</link>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:570
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tabulators and Spaces"
msgstr "Tabulatorji in presledki"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:572
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When this is enabled, the editor will insert spaces as describe above when "
"indenting or pressing &Tab; at the beginning of a line, but insert "
"tabulators when the &Tab; key is pressed in the middle or end of a line."
msgstr ""
"Ko je to omogočeno, bo urejevalnik vstavil presledke, kot je opisano zgoraj, "
"ko zamika ali pritisne &Tab; na začetku vrstice, vendar vstavite "
"tabulatorje, ko &Tab; je tipka pritisnjena na sredini ali koncu vrstice."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:578
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tab width:"
msgstr "Širina zavihka:"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:580
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This configures the number of spaces that are displayed in place of a "
"tabulator character."
msgstr ""
"To konfigurira število presledkov, ki so prikazani namesto znaka tabulatorja."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:585
#, no-c-format
msgid "Indentation width:"
msgstr "Širina vdolbine:"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:587
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The indentation width is the number of spaces which is used to indent a "
"line. If configured to indent using tabulators, a tabulator character is "
"inserted if the indentation is divisible by the tab width."
msgstr ""
"Širina zamika je število presledkov, ki se uporabljajo za zamik vrstice. Če "
"je konfiguriran za zamik z uporabo tabulatorjev, se znak tabulatorja vstavi, "
"če je zamik deljiv s širino zavihka."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:597
#, no-c-format
msgid "Indentation Properties"
msgstr "Lastnosti zamika"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:601
#, no-c-format
msgid "Keep extra spaces"
msgstr "Ohranite dodatne prostore"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:602
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is disabled, changing the indentation level aligns a line to "
"a multiple of the width specified in <guilabel>Indentation width</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost onemogočena, spreminjanje ravni zamika poravna črto na "
"večkratnik širine, določene v <guilabel>Širina zamika</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:607
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adjust indentation of text pasted from the clipboard"
msgstr "Prilagodite zamik besedila, prilepljenega iz odložišča"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:609
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is selected, text pasted from the clipboard is indented. "
"Triggering the <guimenuitem>Undo</guimenuitem> action removes the "
"indentation."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete to možnost, je besedilo, prilepljeno iz odložišča, zamaknjeno. "
"Sprožitev dejanja <guimenuitem>Razveljavi</guimenuitem> odstrani zamik."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:618
#, no-c-format
msgid "Indentation Actions"
msgstr "Dejanja zamika"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:622
#, no-c-format
msgid "Backspace key in leading blank space unindents"
msgstr "Tipka vračalka v začetni prazen prostor odstrani zamike"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:624
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is selected, the &Backspace; key decreases the indentation "
"level if the cursor is located in the leading blank space of a line."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost izbrana, se tipka &Backspace; tipka zmanjša stopnjo zamika, "
"če se kazalec nahaja na prvem praznem mestu vrstice."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:629
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tab key action (if no selection exists)"
msgstr "Dejanje tipke Tab (če ni izbire)"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:631
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want &Tab; to align the current line in the current code block like "
"in &Emacs;, make &Tab; a shortcut to the action <guimenuitem>Format "
"Indentation</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite &Tab; da poravnate trenutno vrstico v trenutnem bloku kode, kot v "
"&Emacs;, naredite &Tab; bližnjica do dejanja <guimenuitem>Oblika zamika</"
"guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:637
#, no-c-format
msgid "Always advance to the next tab position"
msgstr "Vedno se pomaknite na naslednji položaj zavihka"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:639
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is selected, the &Tab; key always inserts white space so that "
"the next tab position is reached. If the option <guilabel>Insert spaces "
"instead of tabulators</guilabel> on the <guilabel>General</guilabel> tab in "
"the <guilabel>Editing</guilabel> page is enabled, spaces are inserted; "
"otherwise, a single tabulator is inserted."
msgstr ""
"Če je izbrana ta možnost, se &Tab; tipka vedno vstavi prazen prostor, tako "
"da je dosežen naslednji položaj zavihka. Če je možnost <guilabel>Vstavi "
"presledke namesto tabulatorjev</guilabel> na zavihku <guilabel>Splošno</"
"guilabel> na strani <guilabel>Urejanje</guilabel> omogočena, se presledki "
"vstavijo; drugače je vstavljen en tabulator."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:646
#, no-c-format
msgid "Always increase indentation level"
msgstr "Vedno povečajte stopnjo zamika"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:648
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is selected, the &Tab; key always indents the current line by "
"the number of character positions specified in <guilabel>Indentation width</"
"guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Če je izbrana ta možnost, se &Tab; tipka vedno zamakne trenutno vrstico za "
"število položajev znakov, določenih v <guilabel>Širina zamika</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:654
#, no-c-format
msgid "Increase indentation level if in leading blank space"
msgstr "Povečajte stopnjo zamika, če je na začetku prazen prostor"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:656
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is selected, the &Tab; key either indents the current line or "
"advances to the next tab position. If the insertion point is at or before "
"the first non-space character in the line, or if there is a selection, the "
"current line is indented by the number of character positions specified in "
"<guilabel>Indentation width</guilabel>. If the insertion point is located "
"after the first non-space character in the line and there is no selection, "
"white space is inserted so that the next tab position is reached: if the "
"option <guilabel>Insert spaces instead of tabulators</guilabel> on the "
"<guilabel>General</guilabel> tab in the <guilabel>Editing</guilabel> page is "
"enabled, spaces are inserted; otherwise, a single tabulator is inserted."
msgstr ""
"Če je izbrana ta možnost, se &Tab; tipka zamakne trenutno vrstico ali se "
"premakne na naslednji položaj zavihka. Če je točka vstavljanja na ali pred "
"prvim znakom, ki ni presledek v vrstici, ali če obstaja izbor, je trenutna "
"vrstica zamaknjena s številom položajev znakov, določenim v <guilabel>Širina "
"zamika</guilabel>. Če je točka vstavljanja za prvim znakom, ki ni presledek "
"v vrstici, in ni izbire, se vstavi prazen prostor, tako da je dosežen "
"naslednji položaj zavihka: če je možnost <guilabel>Vstavi presledke namesto "
"tabulatorjev</guilabel> na zavihku <guilabel>Splošno</guilabel> na strani "
"<guilabel>Urejanje</guilabel> je omogočeno, presledki so vstavljeni; drugače "
"je vstavljen en tabulator."

#. Tag: title
#: configuring.docbook:680
#, no-c-format
msgid "Auto Completion"
msgstr "Samodejno dokončanje"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:683 configuring.docbook:741
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>General</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Splošno</guilabel>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:687
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable auto completion"
msgstr "Omogoči samodejno dokončanje"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:689
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If enabled, a word completion box automatically pops up during typing "
"showing a list of text entries to complete the current text under the cursor."
msgstr ""
"Če je omogočeno, se med tipkanjem samodejno pojavi polje za dokončanje "
"besed, ki prikazuje seznam besedilnih vnosov za dokončanje trenutnega "
"besedila pod kazalko."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:695
#, no-c-format
msgid "Auto select first completion entry"
msgstr "Samodejna izbira prvega zaključnega vnosa"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:697
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If enabled, the first auto completion item is always preselected so you can "
"insert it with &Enter;. If you do not want such behavior, &eg; if you want "
"pressing &Enter; to only insert a newline, then disable this item."
msgstr ""
"Če je omogočeno, je prvi element samodokončanja vedno vnaprej izbran, tako "
"da ga lahko vstavite z &Enter;. Če ne želite takšnega vedenja, &eg; če "
"želite pritisniti &Enter; če želite samo vstaviti novo vrstico, nato "
"onemogočite ta element."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:707
#, no-c-format
msgid "Minimal word length to complete"
msgstr "Najmanjša dolžina besede za dokončanje"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:708
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"While typing text, the word completion searches for words in the document "
"starting with the already typed text. This option configures the minimal "
"amount of characters that are needed to make the word completion active and "
"pop up a completion box."
msgstr ""
"Med vnašanjem besedila dopolnjevanje besed išče besede v dokumentu, ki se "
"začnejo z že vnesenim besedilom. Ta možnost konfigurira minimalno število "
"znakov, ki so potrebni, da postane dopolnjevanje besed aktivno in se prikaže "
"okno za dopolnjevanje."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:715
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove tail on complete"
msgstr "Ko končate, odstranite rep"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:716
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Remove the tail of a previous word when the completion item is chosen from a "
"list."
msgstr ""
"Odstrani rep prejšnje besede, ko je element za dokončanje izbran s seznama."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:721
#, no-c-format
msgid "Keyword completion"
msgstr "Dokončanje ključne besede"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:723
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If enabled, the built-in autocompletion uses the keywords defined by the "
"syntax highlighting."
msgstr ""
"Če je omogočeno, vgrajeno samodokončanje uporablja ključne besede, ki jih "
"določa označevanje sintakse."

#. Tag: title
#: configuring.docbook:732
#, no-c-format
msgid "Spellcheck"
msgstr "Preverjanje črkovanja"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:733
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These configuration options are described in the documentation for the "
"&systemsettings; module <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/spellchecking\">Spell "
"Checker</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Te konfiguracijske možnosti so opisane v dokumentaciji za &systemsettings; "
"modul <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/spellchecking\">Črkovalnik</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: configuring.docbook:738
#, no-c-format
msgid "Vi Input Mode"
msgstr "Način vnosa Vi"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:745
#, no-c-format
msgid "Let Vi commands override Kate shortcuts"
msgstr "Naj ukazi Vi preglasijo bližnjice Kate"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:747
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When selected, Vi commands will override &kappname;'s built-in commands. For "
"example: <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo> will "
"redo, and override the standard action (showing the search and replace "
"dialog)."
msgstr ""
"Ko izberete, bodo ukazi Vi preglasili vgrajene ukaze &kappname;. Na primer: "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo> bo ponovil in "
"preglasil standardno dejanje (prikaz pogovornega okna za iskanje in "
"zamenjavo)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:753
#, no-c-format
msgid "Display relative line numbers"
msgstr "Prikaz relativnih številk vrstic"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:755
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"if this is enabled, the current line always refers to line 0. Lines above "
"and below increase the line number relatively."
msgstr ""
"če je to omogočeno, se trenutna vrstica vedno nanaša na vrstico 0. Vrstici "
"zgoraj in spodaj relativno povečata številko vrstice."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:762
#, no-c-format
msgid "Key Mapping"
msgstr "Preslikava ključev"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:763
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Key mapping is used to change the meaning of typed keys. This allows you to "
"move commands to other keys or make special keypresses for doing a series of "
"commands."
msgstr ""
"Preslikava tipk se uporablja za spreminjanje pomena vnesenih tipk. To vam "
"omogoča premikanje ukazov na druge tipke ali posebne pritiske tipk za "
"izvajanje niza ukazov."

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:767
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example:"
msgstr "Primer:"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:768
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>F2</keycap> -> <userinput>I--</userinput> &Esc;"
msgstr "<keycap>F2</keycap> -> <userinput>I--</userinput> &Esc;"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:769
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will prepend <userinput>I--</userinput> to a line when pressing "
"<keycap>F2</keycap>."
msgstr ""
"To bo pred vrstico dodalo <userinput>IN--</userinput>, ko pritisnete "
"<keycap>F2</keycap>."

#. Tag: title
#: configuring.docbook:783
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open/Save"
msgstr "Odpri/Shrani"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:791
#, no-c-format
msgid "File Format"
msgstr "Format datoteke"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:796
#, no-c-format
msgid "Encoding"
msgstr "Kodiranje"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:798
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This defines the standard encoding to use to open/save files, if not changed "
"in the open/save dialog or by using a command line option."
msgstr ""
"To definira standardno kodiranje za odpiranje/shranjevanje datotek, če ni "
"spremenjeno v pogovornem oknu za odpiranje/shranjevanje ali z uporabo "
"možnosti ukazne vrstice."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:804
#, no-c-format
msgid "Encoding Detection"
msgstr "Zaznavanje kodiranja"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:806
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select an item from the drop down box, either to disable autodetection or "
"use <guilabel>Universal</guilabel> to enable autodetection for all "
"encodings. But as this may probably only detect utf-8/utf-16, selecting a "
"region will use custom heuristics for better results. If neither the "
"encoding chosen as standard above, nor the encoding specified in the open/"
"save dialog, nor the encoding specified on command line match the content of "
"the file, this detection will be run."
msgstr ""
"V spustnem polju izberite element, da onemogočite samodejno zaznavanje ali "
"uporabite <guilabel>Univerzalno</guilabel>, da omogočite samodejno "
"zaznavanje za vsa kodiranja. Ker pa to verjetno zazna samo utf-8/utf-16, bo "
"izbira regije za boljše rezultate uporabila hevristiko po meri. Če se niti "
"zgoraj izbrano standardno kodiranje, niti kodiranje, določeno v pogovornem "
"oknu za odpiranje/shranjevanje, niti kodiranje, določeno v ukazni vrstici, "
"ne ujemajo z vsebino datoteke, se bo zagnalo to zaznavanje."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:817
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fallback Encoding"
msgstr "Nadomestno kodiranje"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:819
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This defines the fallback encoding to try for opening files if neither the "
"encoding chosen as standard above, nor the encoding specified in the open/ "
"save dialog, nor the encoding specified on command line match the content of "
"the file. Before this is used, an attempt will be made to determine the "
"encoding to use by looking for a byte order mark at start of file: if one is "
"found, the right unicode encoding will be chosen; otherwise encoding "
"detection will run, if both fail fallback encoding will be tried."
msgstr ""
"To definira nadomestno kodiranje za poskus odpiranja datotek, če se niti "
"kodiranje, izbrano kot standardno zgoraj, niti kodiranje, določeno v "
"pogovornem oknu za odpiranje/shranjevanje, niti kodiranje, določeno v ukazni "
"vrstici, ne ujemajo z vsebino datoteke. Preden se to uporabi, se bo "
"poskusilo določiti kodiranje za uporabo z iskanjem oznake vrstnega reda "
"bajtov na začetku datoteke: če je najdena, bo izbrano pravo kodiranje "
"unicode; sicer se bo zagnalo zaznavanje kodiranja, če oba ne uspeta, se bo "
"poskusilo nadomestno kodiranje."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:830
#, no-c-format
msgid "End of line"
msgstr "Konec vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:832
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose your preferred end of line mode for your active document. You have "
"the choice between &UNIX;, DOS/&Windows; or Macintosh."
msgstr ""
"Izberite želeni način konca vrstice za vaš aktivni dokument. Izbirate lahko "
"med &UNIX;, DOS/&Windows; ali Macintosh."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:837
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatic end of line detection"
msgstr "Samodejno zaznavanje konca vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:839
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this if you want the editor to autodetect the end of line type. The "
"first found end of line type will be used for the whole file."
msgstr ""
"Označite to, če želite, da urejevalnik samodejno zazna vrsto konca vrstice. "
"Prva najdena vrsta konca vrstice bo uporabljena za celotno datoteko."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:845
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable byte order mark (BOM)"
msgstr "Omogoči oznako vrstnega reda bajtov (BOM)"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:847
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The byte order mark is a special sequence at the beginning of unicode "
"encoded documents. It helps editors to open text documents with the correct "
"unicode encoding. For more information see <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia."
"org/wiki/Byte_order_mark\">Byte Order Mark</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Oznaka vrstnega reda bajtov je posebno zaporedje na začetku dokumentov, "
"kodiranih z Unicode. Urednikom pomaga odpreti besedilne dokumente s "
"pravilnim kodiranjem unicode. Za več informacij glejte <ulink url=\"https://"
"en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Byte_order_mark\">Oznaka vrstnega reda bajtov</ulink>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:855
#, no-c-format
msgid "Line Length Limit"
msgstr "Omejitev dolžine vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:857
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Unfortunately, due to deficiencies in &Qt;, &kappname; experiences poor "
"performance when working with extremely long lines. For that reason, "
"&kappname; will automatically wrap lines when they are longer than the "
"number of characters specified here. To disable this, set this to "
"<userinput>0</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Na žalost zaradi pomanjkljivosti v &Qt;, &kappname; ima slabo delovanje pri "
"delu z izjemno dolgimi linijami. Iz tega razloga &kappname; bo samodejno "
"prelomil vrstice, ko bodo daljše od tukaj navedenega števila znakov. Če "
"želite to onemogočiti, nastavite to na <userinput>0</userinput>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:869
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatic Cleanups on Save"
msgstr "Samodejna čiščenja ob shranjevanju"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:874
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove trailing spaces"
msgstr "Odstranite končne presledke"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:876
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The editor will automatically eliminate extra spaces at the ends of lines of "
"text while saving the file. You can select <guilabel>Never</guilabel> to "
"disable this functionality, <guilabel>On Modified Lines</guilabel> to do so "
"only on lines that you have modified since you last saved the document, or "
"<guilabel>In Entire Document</guilabel> to remove them unconditionally from "
"the entire document."
msgstr ""
"Urejevalnik bo med shranjevanjem datoteke samodejno odstranil dodatne "
"presledke na koncih vrstic besedila. Izberete lahko <guilabel>Nikoli</"
"guilabel>, da onemogočite to funkcijo, <guilabel>V spremenjenih vrsticah</"
"guilabel>, da to storite samo v vrsticah, ki ste jih spremenili od zadnjega "
"shranjevanja dokumenta, ali <guilabel>V celotnem dokumentu </guilabel>, da "
"jih brezpogojno odstranite iz celotnega dokumenta."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:886
#, no-c-format
msgid "Append newline at end of file on save"
msgstr "Pri shranjevanju dodajte novo vrstico na konec datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:888
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The editor will automatically append a newline to the end of the file if one "
"is not already present upon saving the file."
msgstr ""
"Urejevalnik bo samodejno dodal novo vrstico na konec datoteke, če ta še ni "
"prisotna ob shranjevanju datoteke."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:898
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable Auto Save (local files only)"
msgstr "Omogoči samodejno shranjevanje (samo lokalne datoteke)"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:900
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this if you want the editor to autosave documents while you are "
"working on them."
msgstr ""
"Označite to, če želite, da urejevalnik samodejno shrani dokumente, medtem ko "
"delate na njih."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:906
#, no-c-format
msgid "Auto save document when focus leaves the editor"
msgstr "Samodejno shrani dokument, ko fokus zapusti urejevalnik"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:908
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The editor will automatically save documents when you switch to something "
"outside the editor, &eg;, the terminal panel in &kate;."
msgstr ""
"Urejevalnik bo samodejno shranil dokumente, ko preklopite na nekaj zunaj "
"urejevalnika, &eg; terminalsko ploščo v &kate;."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:913
#, no-c-format
msgid "Auto save interval"
msgstr "Interval samodejnega shranjevanja"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:915
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can determine the autosave interval in seconds here. If the interval is "
"0, the document will not be autosaved after intervals."
msgstr ""
"Tu lahko določite interval samodejnega shranjevanja v sekundah. Če je "
"interval 0, se dokument po intervalih ne bo samodejno shranil."

#. Tag: title
#: configuring.docbook:927
#, no-c-format
msgid "Advanced"
msgstr "Napredno"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:931
#, no-c-format
msgid "Write a backup file on save for"
msgstr "Napišite datoteko varnostne kopije pri shranjevanju za"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:932
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Backing up on save will cause &kappname; to copy the disk file (the "
"previously saved version of the file) to &lt;prefix&gt;&lt;filename&gt;&lt;"
"suffix&gt; before saving the new changes. A backup file can help you recover "
"work if something goes wrong while saving or if you later want to recover "
"the previous version of the file. The suffix defaults to <emphasis role="
"\"bold\">~</emphasis> and prefix is empty by default."
msgstr ""
"Varnostno kopiranje ob shranjevanju bo povzročilo &kappname; da kopirate "
"diskovno datoteko (prejšnjo shranjeno različico datoteke) v &lt;predpono&gt;"
"&lt;ime datoteke&gt;&lt;pripono&gt; preden shranite nove spremembe. "
"Varnostna kopija datoteke vam lahko pomaga obnoviti delo, če gre med "
"shranjevanjem kaj narobe ali če želite pozneje obnoviti prejšnjo različico "
"datoteke. Pripona je privzeto <emphasis role=\"bold\">~</emphasis>, predpona "
"pa je privzeto prazna."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:940
#, no-c-format
msgid "Local files"
msgstr "Lokalne datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:942
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check this if you want backups of local files when saving."
msgstr ""
"Označite to, če želite pri shranjevanju varnostne kopije lokalnih datotek."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:947
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remote files"
msgstr "Oddaljene datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:949
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check this if you want backups of remote files when saving."
msgstr ""
"Označite to, če želite pri shranjevanju varnostne kopije oddaljenih datotek."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:953
#, no-c-format
msgid "Prefix for backup files"
msgstr "Predpona za varnostne kopije datotek"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:955
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enter the prefix to prepend to the backup file names."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite predpono, ki jo želite dodati pred imena datotek varnostne kopije."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:959
#, no-c-format
msgid "Suffix for backup files"
msgstr "Pripona za varnostne kopije datotek"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:961
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enter the suffix to add to the backup file names."
msgstr "Vnesite pripono, ki jo želite dodati imenom datotek varnostne kopije."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:965
#, no-c-format
msgid "Swap file mode"
msgstr "Način izmenjave datotek"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:967
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kappname; is able to recover (most) unsaved work in the case of a crash or "
"power failure. A swap file (.&lt;filename&gt;.kate-swp) is created when a "
"document is edited. If the user doesn’t save the changes and &kappname; "
"crashes, the swap file remains on the disk. When opening a file, &kappname; "
"checks if there is a swap file for the document and if it is, it asks the "
"user whether he wants to recover the lost data or not. The user has the "
"possibility to view the differences between the original file and the "
"recovered one, too. The swap file is deleted after every save and on normal "
"exit."
msgstr ""
"&kappname; lahko obnovi (večino) neshranjenega dela v primeru zrušitve ali "
"izpada električne energije. Izmenjalna datoteka (.&lt;filename&gt;.kate-swp) "
"se ustvari, ko je dokument urejen. Če uporabnik ne shrani sprememb in "
"&kappname; zruši, izmenjalna datoteka ostane na disku. Ko odprete datoteko, "
"&kappname; preveri ali obstaja izmenjalna datoteka za dokument in če "
"obstaja, vpraša uporabnika ali želi obnoviti izgubljene podatke ali ne. "
"Uporabnik ima možnost videti tudi razlike med izvirno in obnovljeno "
"datoteko. Izmenjalna datoteka se izbriše po vsakem shranjevanju in ob "
"običajnem izhodu."

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:975
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kappname; syncs the swap files on the disk every 15 seconds, but only if "
"they have changed since the last sync. The user can disable the swap files "
"syncing if he wants, by selecting <guilabel>Disable</guilabel>, but this can "
"lead to more data loss."
msgstr ""
"&kappname; sinhronizira izmenjevalne datoteke na disku vsakih 15 sekund, "
"vendar le, če so bile od zadnje sinhronizacije spremenjene. Uporabnik lahko "
"onemogoči sinhronizacijo izmenjalnih datotek, če želi, tako da izbere "
"<guilabel>Onemogoči</guilabel>, vendar lahko to povzroči večjo izgubo "
"podatkov."

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:979
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the swap file is enabled, it is possible to switch between two modes, "
"namely <guilabel>Enabled, Store in Default Directory</guilabel> and "
"<guilabel>Enabled, Store in Custom Directory</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Ko je izmenjalna datoteka omogočena, je mogoče preklapljati med dvema "
"načinoma, in sicer <guilabel>Omogočeno, Shrani v privzeti imenik</guilabel> "
"in <guilabel>Omogočeno, Shrani v imenik po meri</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:984
#, no-c-format
msgid "Store swap files in"
msgstr "Shranite izmenjalne datoteke v"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:985
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default, the swap files are saved in the same folder as the file. When "
"<guilabel>Enabled, Store in Custom Directory</guilabel> is chosen for the "
"swap file mode, swap files are created in the specified folder. This is "
"useful for network file systems to avoid unnecessary network traffic."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto so izmenjalne datoteke shranjene v isto mapo kot datoteka. Ko je za "
"način izmenjalne datoteke izbrano <guilabel>Omogočeno, shrani v imenik po "
"meri</guilabel>, se izmenjalne datoteke ustvarijo v navedeni mapi. To je "
"uporabno za omrežne datotečne sisteme, da se izognete nepotrebnemu omrežnemu "
"prometu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:991
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save swap files every"
msgstr "Shrani izmenjalne datoteke vsak"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:992
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kappname; syncs the swap files on the disk every 15 seconds, but only if "
"they have changed since the last sync. You can change the sync interval as "
"you like."
msgstr ""
"&kappname; sinhronizira izmenjevalne datoteke na disku vsakih 15 sekund, "
"vendar le, če so bile od zadnje sinhronizacije spremenjene. Interval "
"sinhronizacije lahko spremenite po želji."

#. Tag: title
#: configuring.docbook:1004
#, no-c-format
msgid "Modes &amp; Filetypes"
msgstr "Načini &amp; Vrste datotek"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1005
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This page allows you to override the default configuration for documents of "
"specified &MIME; types. When the editor loads a document, it will try if it "
"matches the file masks or &MIME; types for one of the defined filetypes, and "
"if so apply the variables defined. If more filetypes match, the one with the "
"highest priority will be used."
msgstr ""
"Ta stran vam omogoča, da preglasite privzeto konfiguracijo za dokumente "
"določenega &MIME; vrste. Ko urejevalnik naloži dokument, bo poskusil, ali se "
"ujema z datotečnimi maskami ali &MIME; vrste za eno od definiranih vrst "
"datotek, in če je tako, uporabite definirane spremenljivke. Če se ujema več "
"vrst datotek, bo uporabljena tista z najvišjo prioriteto."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:1013
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filetype:"
msgstr "Vrsta datoteke:"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1014 configuring.docbook:1034
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The filetype with the highest priority is the one displayed in the first "
"drop down box. If more filetypes were found, they are also listed."
msgstr ""
"Vrsta datoteke z najvišjo prioriteto je tista, ki je prikazana v prvem "
"spustnem polju. Če je bilo najdenih več vrst datotek, so tudi te navedene."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:1019
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>New</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Novo</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1020
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is used to create a new filetype. After you click on this button, the "
"fields below get empty and you can fill the properties you want for the new "
"filetype."
msgstr ""
"To se uporablja za ustvarjanje nove vrste datoteke. Ko kliknete ta gumb, se "
"spodnja polja izpraznijo in lahko izpolnite lastnosti, ki jih želite za novo "
"vrsto datoteke."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:1025
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete"
msgstr "Izbriši"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1026
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To remove an existing filetype, select it from the drop down box and press "
"the Delete button."
msgstr ""
"Če želite odstraniti obstoječo vrsto datoteke, jo izberite v spustnem meniju "
"in pritisnite gumb Izbriši."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:1033
#, no-c-format
msgid "Properties of <replaceable>current filetype</replaceable>"
msgstr "Lastnosti <replaceable>trenutne vrste datoteke</replaceable>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:1039
#, no-c-format
msgid "Name:"
msgstr "Ime:"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1040
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The name of the filetype will be the text of the corresponding menu item. "
"This name is displayed in the <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Filetypes</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> menu."
msgstr ""
"Ime vrste datoteke bo besedilo ustrezne menijske postavke. To ime je "
"prikazano v meniju <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Vrste "
"datotek</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:1046
#, no-c-format
msgid "Section:"
msgstr "Razdelek:"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1047
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The section name is used to organize the file types in menus. This is also "
"used in the <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Filetypes</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> menu."
msgstr ""
"Ime razdelka se uporablja za organiziranje vrst datotek v menijih. To se "
"uporablja tudi v meniju <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Vrste datotek</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:1053
#, no-c-format
msgid "Variables:"
msgstr "Spremenljivke:"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1054
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This string allows you to configure &kappname;'s settings for the files "
"selected by this &MIME; type using &kappname; variables. You can set almost "
"any configuration option, such as highlight, indent-mode, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"Ta niz vam omogoča, da konfigurirate nastavitve &kappname; za datoteke, ki "
"jih izbere ta &MIME; tipkajte z &kappname; spremenljivke. Nastavite lahko "
"skoraj vse možnosti konfiguracije, kot so osvetlitev, način zamika &etc;"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1057
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press <guibutton>Edit</guibutton> to see a list of all available variables "
"and their descriptions. Select the checkbox on the left to enable a "
"particular variable and then set the value of the variable on the right. "
"Some variables provide a drop-down box to select possible values from while "
"others require you to enter a valid value manually."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite <guibutton>Uredi</guibutton> za ogled seznama vseh razpoložljivih "
"spremenljivk in njihovih opisov. Izberite potrditveno polje na levi, da "
"omogočite določeno spremenljivko, nato pa nastavite vrednost spremenljivke "
"na desni. Nekatere spremenljivke ponujajo spustno polje za izbiro možnih "
"vrednosti, druge pa zahtevajo, da veljavno vrednost vnesete ročno."

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1062
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For complete information on these variables, see <link linkend=\"config-"
"variables\">Configuring with Document Variables</link>."
msgstr ""
"Za popolne informacije o teh spremenljivkah glejte <link linkend=\"config-"
"variables\">Konfiguriranje s spremenljivkami dokumenta</link>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:1069
#, no-c-format
msgid "Highlighting:"
msgstr "Označevanje:"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1070
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you create a new file type, this drop down box allows you to select a "
"filetype for highlighting."
msgstr ""
"Če ustvarite novo vrsto datoteke, vam ta spustni meni omogoča izbiro vrste "
"datoteke za označevanje."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:1075
#, no-c-format
msgid "Indentation Mode:"
msgstr "Način zamika:"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1076
#, no-c-format
msgid "The drop down box specifies the indentation mode for new documents."
msgstr "Spustno polje določa način zamika za nove dokumente."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:1081
#, no-c-format
msgid "File extensions:"
msgstr "Pripone datotek:"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1082
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The wildcards mask allows you to select files by filename. A typical mask "
"uses an asterisk and the file extension, for example <filename>*.txt; *."
"text</filename>. The string is a semicolon-separated list of masks."
msgstr ""
"Maska nadomestnih znakov omogoča izbiro datotek po imenu datoteke. Tipična "
"maska uporablja zvezdico in pripono datoteke, na primer <filename>*.txt; *."
"text</filename>. Niz je s podpičjem ločen seznam mask."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:1089
#, no-c-format
msgid "MIME types:"
msgstr "Vrste MIME:"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1090
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displays a wizard that helps you easily select &MIME; types."
msgstr "Prikaže čarovnika, ki vam pomaga enostavno izbrati &MIME; vrste."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: configuring.docbook:1095
#, no-c-format
msgid "Priority:"
msgstr "Prednost:"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1096
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sets a priority for this file type. If more than one file type selects the "
"same file, the one with the highest priority will be used."
msgstr ""
"Nastavi prednost za to vrsto datoteke. Če več kot ena vrsta datoteke izbere "
"isto datoteko, bo uporabljena tista z najvišjo prioriteto."

#. Tag: title
#: configuring.docbook:1112
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring With Document Variables"
msgstr "Konfiguriranje s spremenljivkami dokumenta"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kappname; variables is &kappname;'s implementation of document variables, "
"similar to &Emacs; and vi modelines. In katepart, the lines have the "
"following format: <userinput>kate: VARIABLENAME VALUE; [ VARIABLENAME "
"VALUE; ... ]</userinput> The lines can of course be in a comment, if the "
"file is in a format with comments. Variable names are single words (no "
"whitespace), and anything up to the next semicolon is the value. The "
"semicolon is required."
msgstr ""
"&kappname; variables je implementacija spremenljivk dokumenta &kappname;, "
"podobna &Emacs; in vi modelines. V katepartu imajo vrstice naslednjo obliko: "
"<userinput>kate: VARIABLENAME VALUE; [ VREDNOST IME SPREMENLJIVKE; ... ]</"
"userinput> Vrstice so seveda lahko v komentarju, če je datoteka v formatu s "
"komentarji. Imena spremenljivk so posamezne besede (brez presledkov) in vse "
"do naslednjega podpičja je vrednost. Podpičje je obvezno."

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here is an example variable line, forcing indentation settings for a C++, "
"&Java; or &javascript; file:"
msgstr ""
"Tukaj je primer spremenljivke, ki vsiljuje nastavitve zamika za C++, &Java; "
"ali &javascript; mapa:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: configuring.docbook:1126
#, no-c-format
msgid "// kate: replace-tabs on; indent-width 4; indent-mode cstyle;"
msgstr "// kate: zamenjaj zavihke na; širina zamika 4; način zamika cstyle;"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1129
#, no-c-format
msgid "Only the first and last 10 lines are searched for variable lines."
msgstr "Spremenljive vrstice se iščejo le v prvih in zadnjih 10 vrsticah."

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally, document variables can be placed in a file called <filename>."
"kateconfig</filename> in any directory, and the configured settings will be "
"applied as if the modelines were entered on every file in the directory and "
"its subdirectories. Document variables in <filename>.kateconfig</filename> "
"use the same syntax as in modelines, but with <link linkend=\"kateconfig-"
"extended-options\">extended options</link>."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega lahko spremenljivke dokumenta postavite v datoteko z imenom "
"<filename>.kateconfig</filename> v katerem koli imeniku in konfigurirane "
"nastavitve bodo uporabljene, kot da bi bili modeli vneseni v vsako datoteko "
"v imeniku in njegovih podimenikih. Spremenljivke dokumenta v <filename>."
"kateconfig</filename> uporabljajo isto sintakso kot v modelines, vendar z "
"<link linkend=\"kateconfig-extended-options\">razširjenimi možnostmi</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1137
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are variables to support almost all configurations in &kappname;, and "
"additionally plugins can use variables, in which case it should be "
"documented in the plugin's documentation."
msgstr ""
"V &kappname; obstajajo spremenljivke, ki podpirajo skoraj vse konfiguracije, "
"poleg tega pa lahko vtičniki uporabljajo spremenljivke; v tem primeru mora "
"biti to dokumentirano v dokumentaciji vtičnika."

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1141
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kappname; has support for reading configurations from <filename>."
"editorconfig</filename> files, when the <ulink url=\"https://editorconfig."
"org/\">editorconfig</ulink> library is installed. &kappname; automatically "
"searches for a <filename>.editorconfig</filename> whenever you open a file. "
"It gives priority to <filename>.kateconfig</filename> files, though."
msgstr ""
"&kappname; ima podporo za branje konfiguracij iz datotek <filename>."
"editorconfig</filename>, ko je nameščena knjižnica <ulink url=\"https://"
"editorconfig.org/\">editorconfig</ulink>. &kappname; samodejno poišče "
"<filename>.editorconfig</filename> vsakič, ko odprete datoteko. Vendar daje "
"prednost datotekam <filename>.kateconfig</filename>."

#. Tag: title
#: configuring.docbook:1148
#, no-c-format
msgid "How &kappname; uses Variables"
msgstr "Kako &kappname; uporablja spremenljivke"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1150
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When reading configuration, katepart looks in the following places (in that "
"order): <itemizedlist> <listitem><para>The global configuration.</para></"
"listitem> <listitem><para>Optional session data.</para></listitem> "
"<listitem><para>The \"Filetype\" configuration.</para></listitem> "
"<listitem><para>Document variables in <filename>.kateconfig</filename>.</"
"para></listitem> <listitem><para>Document variables in the document itself.</"
"para></listitem> <listitem><para>Settings made during editing from menu or "
"command line.</para></listitem> </itemizedlist> As you can see, document "
"variables are only overridden by changes made at runtime. Whenever a "
"document is saved, the document variables are reread, and will overwrite "
"changes made using menu items or the command line."
msgstr ""
"Ko bere konfiguracijo, katepart išče na naslednjih mestih (v tem vrstnem "
"redu): <itemizedlist> <listitem><para>Globalna konfiguracija.</para></"
"listitem> <listitem><para>Izbirni podatki o seji.</para ></listitem> "
"<listitem><para>Konfiguracija \"Vrsta datoteke\".</para></listitem> "
"<listitem><para>Spremenljivke dokumenta v <filename>.kateconfig</filename>.</"
"para></listitem> <listitem><para>Spremenljivke dokumenta v samem dokumentu.</"
"para></listitem> <listitem><para>Nastavitve med urejanjem iz menija ali "
"ukazne vrstice.</para></listitem> </itemizedlist > Kot lahko vidite, "
"spremenljivke dokumenta preglasijo samo spremembe, ki so narejene med "
"izvajanjem. Kadarkoli je dokument shranjen, se spremenljivke dokumenta "
"ponovno preberejo in prepišejo spremembe, narejene z uporabo elementov "
"menija ali ukazne vrstice."

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1166
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Any variable not listed below is stored in the document and can be queried "
"by other objects such as plugins, which can use them for their own purpose. "
"For example, the variable indent mode uses document variables for its "
"configuration."
msgstr ""
"Vsaka spremenljivka, ki ni navedena spodaj, je shranjena v dokumentu in po "
"njej lahko poizvedujejo drugi objekti, kot so vtičniki, ki jih lahko "
"uporabljajo za lastne namene. Na primer, način spremenljivega zamika za "
"svojo konfiguracijo uporablja spremenljivke dokumenta."

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1171
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The variables listed here documents &kappname; version 5.38. More variables "
"may be added in the future. There are 3 possible types of values for "
"variables, with the following valid expressions:"
msgstr ""
"Tukaj navedene spremenljivke dokumentirajo &kappname; različica 5.38. V "
"prihodnosti bo morda dodanih več spremenljivk. Obstajajo 3 možne vrste "
"vrednosti za spremenljivke z naslednjimi veljavnimi izrazi:"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1175
#, no-c-format
msgid "BOOL - on|off|true|false|1|0"
msgstr "BOOL - on|off|true|false|1|0"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1176
#, no-c-format
msgid "INTEGER - any integer number"
msgstr "INTEGER - poljubno celo število"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1177
#, no-c-format
msgid "STRING - anything else"
msgstr "STRING – karkoli drugega"

#. Tag: title
#: configuring.docbook:1184
#, no-c-format
msgid "Available Variables"
msgstr "Razpoložljive spremenljivke"

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: configuring.docbook:1189
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>auto-brackets</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"
msgstr "<command>samodejni oklepaji</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1190
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable automatic insertion of brackets."
msgstr "Omogoči samodejno vstavljanje oklepajev."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: configuring.docbook:1194
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>auto-center-lines</command><arg>INT</arg>"
msgstr "<command>samodejne sredinske črte</command><arg>INT</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1195
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set the number of autocenter lines."
msgstr "Nastavite število črt samodejnega središča."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: configuring.docbook:1199
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>background-color</command><arg>STRING</arg>"
msgstr "<command>barva-ozadje</command><arg>STRING</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1200
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the document background color. The value must be something that can be "
"evaluated to a valid color, for example <userinput>#ff0000</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite barvo ozadja dokumenta. Vrednost mora biti nekaj, kar je mogoče "
"ovrednotiti v veljavno barvo, na primer <userinput>#ff0000</userinput>."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: configuring.docbook:1206
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>backspace-indents</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"
msgstr "<command>zamiki-vračalke</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1207
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable or disable unindenting when &Backspace; is pressed."
msgstr ""
"Omogoči ali onemogoči odstranjevanje zamikov, ko &Backspace; je pritisnjen."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: configuring.docbook:1211
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>block-selection</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"
msgstr "<command>izbira bloka</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1212
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Turn <link linkend=\"kate-part-selection-block\">block selection</link> on "
"or off."
msgstr ""
"Vklopite ali izklopite <link linkend=\"kate-part-selection-block\">izbira "
"bloka</link>."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: configuring.docbook:1217
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>bom | byte-order-mark | byte-order-marker</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>bom | byte-order-mark | byte-order-marker</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1218
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enable/disable the byte order mark (BOM) when saving files in Unicode format "
"(utf8, utf16, utf32)."
msgstr ""
"Omogoči/onemogoči oznako vrstnega reda bajtov (BOM) pri shranjevanju datotek "
"v formatu Unicode (utf8, utf16, utf32)."

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1220 configuring.docbook:1240
#, no-c-format
msgid "Since: &kate; 3.4 (&kde; 4.4)"
msgstr "Od: &kate; 3.4 (&kde; 4.4)"

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: configuring.docbook:1224
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>bracket-highlight-color</command><arg>STRING</arg>"
msgstr "<command>oklepaj-poudarjena-barva</command><arg>STRING</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1225
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the color for the bracket highlight. The value must be something that "
"can be evaluated to a valid color, for example <userinput>#ff0000</"
"userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite barvo za osvetlitev oklepaja. Vrednost mora biti nekaj, kar je "
"mogoče ovrednotiti v veljavno barvo, na primer <userinput>#ff0000</"
"userinput>."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: configuring.docbook:1231
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>current-line-color</command><arg>STRING</arg>"
msgstr "<command>trenutna-barva-vrstice</command><arg>STRING</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1232
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the color for the current line. The value must be something that can be "
"evaluated to a valid color, for example <userinput>#ff0000</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite barvo za trenutno vrstico. Vrednost mora biti nekaj, kar je mogoče "
"ovrednotiti v veljavno barvo, na primer <userinput>#ff0000</userinput>."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: configuring.docbook:1238
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>default-dictionary</command><arg>STRING</arg>"
msgstr "<command>privzeti-slovar</command><arg>STRING</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1239
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sets the default dictionary used for spellchecking."
msgstr "Nastavi privzeti slovar za preverjanje črkovanja."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: configuring.docbook:1244
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>dynamic-word-wrap</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"
msgstr "<command>dinamični-prelom-besed</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1245
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Turns <link linkend=\"kate-part-auto-wrap\">dynamic word wrap</link> on or "
"off."
msgstr ""
"Vklopi ali izklopi <link linkend=\"kate-part-auto-wrap\">dinamični prelom "
"besed</link>."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: configuring.docbook:1250
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>eol | end-of-line</command><arg>STRING</arg>"
msgstr "<command>eol | konec vrstice</command><arg>STRING</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1251
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the end of line mode. Valid settings are <userinput>unix</userinput>, "
"<userinput>mac</userinput> and <userinput>dos</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite način konca vrstice. Veljavne nastavitve so <userinput>unix</"
"userinput>, <userinput>mac</userinput> in <userinput>dos</userinput>."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: configuring.docbook:1256
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>folding-markers</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"
msgstr "<command>zložljivi-označevalci</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1257
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the display of <link linkend=\"advanced-editing-tools-code-folding"
"\">folding markers</link> on or off."
msgstr ""
"Vklopite ali izklopite prikaz <link linkend=\"advanced-editing-tools-code-"
"folding\">oznak za zgibanje</link>."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: configuring.docbook:1264
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>folding-preview</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"
msgstr "<command>zlaganje-predogled</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1265
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable folding preview in the editor border."
msgstr "Omogoči predogled zgibanja v obrobi urejevalnika."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: configuring.docbook:1269
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>font-size</command><arg>INT</arg>"
msgstr "<command>velikost pisave</command><arg>INT</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1270
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set the point size of the document font."
msgstr "Nastavite velikost pik pisave dokumenta."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: configuring.docbook:1274
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>font</command><arg>STRING</arg>"
msgstr "<command>pisava</command><arg>STRING</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1275
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the font of the document. The value should be a valid font name, for "
"example <userinput>courier</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite pisavo dokumenta. Vrednost mora biti veljavno ime pisave, na "
"primer <userinput>kurir</userinput>."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: configuring.docbook:1280
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>hl | syntax</command><arg>STRING</arg>"
msgstr "<command>hl | sintaksa</command><arg>STRING</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1281
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the syntax highlighting. Valid strings are all the names available in "
"the menus. For instance, for C++ simply write <userinput>C++</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite označevanje sintakse. Veljavni nizi so vsa imena, ki so na voljo v "
"menijih. Na primer, za C++ preprosto napišite <userinput>C++</userinput>."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: configuring.docbook:1286
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>icon-bar-color</command><arg>STRING</arg>"
msgstr "<command>barva-barve-ikone</command><arg>STRING</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1287
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the icon bar color. The value must be something that can be evaluated to "
"a valid color, for example <userinput>#ff0000</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite barvo vrstice ikon. Vrednost mora biti nekaj, kar je mogoče "
"ovrednotiti v veljavno barvo, na primer <userinput>#ff0000</userinput>."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: configuring.docbook:1292
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>icon-border</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"
msgstr "<command>ikona-obroba</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1293
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set the display of the icon border on or off."
msgstr "Vklopite ali izklopite prikaz obrobe ikone."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: configuring.docbook:1297
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>indent-mode</command><arg>STRING</arg>"
msgstr "<command>način-zamika</command><arg>STRING</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1298
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the auto-indentation mode. The options <userinput>none</userinput>, "
"<userinput>normal</userinput>, <userinput>cstyle</userinput>, "
"<userinput>haskell</userinput>, <userinput>lilypond</userinput>, "
"<userinput>lisp</userinput>, <userinput>python</userinput>, <userinput>ruby</"
"userinput> and <userinput>xml</userinput> are recognized. See the section "
"<xref linkend=\"kate-part-autoindent\"/> for details."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite način samodejnega zamika. Možnosti <userinput>brez</userinput>, "
"<userinput>normalno</userinput>, <userinput>cstyle</userinput>, "
"<userinput>haskell</userinput>, <userinput>lilypond</userinput>, <userinput> "
"lisp</userinput>, <userinput>python</userinput>, <userinput>ruby</userinput> "
"in <userinput>xml</userinput> so prepoznani. Za podrobnosti glejte razdelek "
"<xref linkend=\"kate-part-autoindent\"/>."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: configuring.docbook:1306
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>indent-pasted-text</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"
msgstr "<command>zamik-prilepljeno-besedilo</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1307
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable/disable adjusting indentation of text pasted from the clipboard."
msgstr ""
"Omogoči/onemogoči prilagajanje zamika besedila, prilepljenega iz odložišča."

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1308
#, no-c-format
msgid "Since: &kate; 3.11 (&kde; 4.11)"
msgstr "Od: &kate; 3.11 (&kde; 4.11)"

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: configuring.docbook:1312
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>indent-width</command><arg>INT</arg>"
msgstr "<command>širina-zamika</command><arg>INT</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1313
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set the indentation width."
msgstr "Nastavite širino vdolbine."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: configuring.docbook:1317
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>keep-extra-spaces</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"
msgstr "<command>ohrani-dodatne-prostore</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1318
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set whether to keep extra spaces when calculating indentation width."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite, ali želite obdržati dodatne presledke pri izračunu širine zamika."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: configuring.docbook:1322
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>line-numbers</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"
msgstr "<command>številke vrstic</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1323
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set the display of line numbers on or off."
msgstr "Vklopite ali izklopite prikaz številk vrstic."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: configuring.docbook:1327
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>newline-at-eof</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"
msgstr "<command>nova vrstica-na-eof</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1328
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Add an empty line at the end of the file (EOF) when saving the document."
msgstr ""
"Dodajte prazno vrstico na koncu datoteke (EOF), ko shranjujete dokument."

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1329
#, no-c-format
msgid "Since: &kate; 3.9 (&kde; 4.9)"
msgstr "Od: &kate; 3.9 (&kde; 4.9)"

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: configuring.docbook:1333
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>overwrite-mode</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"
msgstr "<command>način-prepisovanja</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1334
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set overwrite mode on or off."
msgstr "Vklopite ali izklopite način prepisovanja."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: configuring.docbook:1338
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>persistent-selection</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"
msgstr "<command>vztrajna-izbira</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1339
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set <link linkend=\"kate-part-selection-persistent\">persistent selection</"
"link> on or off."
msgstr ""
"Vklopite ali izklopite <link linkend=\"kate-part-selection-persistent"
"\">trajno izbiro</link>."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: configuring.docbook:1344
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>replace-tabs-save</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"
msgstr "<command>zamenjaj-zavihke-shrani</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1345
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set tab to space conversion on save on or off."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite pretvorbo tabulatorja v prostor ob vklopu ali izklopu shranjevanja."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: configuring.docbook:1349
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>replace-tabs</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"
msgstr "<command>zamenjaj zavihke</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1350
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set dynamic tab to space conversion on or off."
msgstr "Vklopite ali izklopite pretvorbo dinamičnega zavihka v prostor."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: configuring.docbook:1354
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>remove-trailing-spaces</command><arg>STRING</arg>"
msgstr "<command>odstrani-končne-presledke</command><arg>STRING</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1355
#, no-c-format
msgid "Removes trailing spaces when saving the document. Valid options are:"
msgstr ""
"Pri shranjevanju dokumenta odstrani končne presledke. Veljavne možnosti so:"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1357
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>none</userinput>, <userinput>-</userinput> or <userinput>0</"
"userinput>: never remove trailing spaces."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>brez</userinput>, <userinput>-</userinput> ali <userinput>0</"
"userinput>: nikoli ne odstranite končnih presledkov."

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1358
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>modified</userinput>, <userinput>mod</userinput>, <userinput>+</"
"userinput> or <userinput>1</userinput>: remove trailing spaces only in "
"modified lines. The modified lines are marked by the line modification "
"system."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>spremenjeno</userinput>, <userinput>mod</userinput>, <userinput>"
"+</userinput> ali <userinput>1</userinput>: odstranite končne presledke samo "
"v spremenjenih vrsticah. Spremenjene črte so označene s sistemom "
"modifikacije linij."

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1360
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>all</userinput>, <userinput>*</userinput> or <userinput>2</"
"userinput>: remove trailing spaces in the entire document."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>vse</userinput>, <userinput>*</userinput> ali <userinput>2</"
"userinput>: odstranite končne presledke v celotnem dokumentu."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: configuring.docbook:1366
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>scrollbar-minimap</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"
msgstr "<command>mini-zemljevid-z-drsnim-trakom</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1367
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show scrollbar minimap."
msgstr "Prikaži mini zemljevid z drsnim trakom."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: configuring.docbook:1371
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>scrollbar-preview</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"
msgstr "<command>predogled-drsnega-traku</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1372
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show scrollbar preview."
msgstr "Prikaži predogled drsnega traku."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: configuring.docbook:1376
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>scheme</command><arg>STRING</arg>"
msgstr "<command>shema</command><arg>STRING</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1377
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the color scheme. The string must be the name of a color scheme that "
"exists in your configuration to have any effect."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite barvno shemo. Niz mora biti ime barvne sheme, ki obstaja v vaši "
"konfiguraciji, da ima učinek."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: configuring.docbook:1382
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>selection-color</command><arg>STRING</arg>"
msgstr "<command>barva-izbora</command><arg>STRING</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1383
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the selection color. The value must be something that can be evaluated "
"to a valid color, for example <userinput>#ff0000</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite barvo izbire. Vrednost mora biti nekaj, kar je mogoče ovrednotiti "
"v veljavno barvo, na primer <userinput>#ff0000</userinput>."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: configuring.docbook:1388
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>show-tabs</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"
msgstr "<command>prikaz-zavihkov</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1389
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set the visual tab character on or off."
msgstr "Vklopite ali izklopite znak vizualnega zavihka."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: configuring.docbook:1393
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>smart-home</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"
msgstr "<command>pametni-dom</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1394
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set <link linkend=\"pref-edit-cursor-selection\">smart home navigation</"
"link> on or off."
msgstr ""
"Vklopite ali izklopite <link linkend=\"pref-edit-cursor-selection"
"\">navigacijo pametnega doma</link>."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: configuring.docbook:1399
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>tab-indents</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"
msgstr "<command>zamiki-zavihkov</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1400
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set &Tab; key indentation on or off."
msgstr "Nastavi &Tab; vklop ali izklop zamika tipk."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: configuring.docbook:1404
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>tab-width</command><arg>INT</arg>"
msgstr "<command>širina zavihka</command><arg>INT</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1405
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set the tab character display width."
msgstr "Nastavite širino prikaza tabulatorskega znaka."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: configuring.docbook:1409
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>undo-steps</command><arg>INT</arg>"
msgstr "<command>razveljavitveni-koraki</command><arg>INT</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1410
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set the number of undo steps to remember."
msgstr "Nastavite število korakov razveljavitve, ki si jih morate zapomniti."

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1411
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note: Deprecated since &kate; 3 in &kde;4. This variable is ignored. The "
"maximal count of undo steps is unlimited."
msgstr ""
"Opomba: Zastarelo od &kate; 3 v &kde;4. Ta spremenljivka je prezrta. "
"Največje število razveljavitvenih korakov je neomejeno."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: configuring.docbook:1415
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>word-wrap-column</command><arg>INT</arg>"
msgstr "<command>stolpec-za-previjanje-besed</command><arg>INT</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1416
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the <link linkend=\"kate-part-auto-wrap\">static word wrap</link> width."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite širino <link linkend=\"kate-part-auto-wrap\">statičnega preloma "
"besed</link>."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: configuring.docbook:1421
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>word-wrap-marker-color</command><arg>STRING</arg>"
msgstr "<command>beseda-prelom-barva-markerja</command><arg>STRING</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1422
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the word wrap marker color. The value must be something that can be "
"evaluated to a valid color, for example <userinput>#ff0000</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite barvo označevalnika za prelom besed. Vrednost mora biti nekaj, kar "
"je mogoče ovrednotiti v veljavno barvo, na primer <userinput>#ff0000</"
"userinput>."

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: configuring.docbook:1427
#, no-c-format
msgid "<command>word-wrap</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"
msgstr "<command>prelom besed</command><arg>BOOL</arg>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1428
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set static word wrapping on or off."
msgstr "Vklopite ali izklopite statično prelivanje besed."

#. Tag: title
#: configuring.docbook:1436
#, no-c-format
msgid "Extended Options in <filename>.kateconfig</filename> files"
msgstr "Razširjene možnosti v datotekah <filename>.kateconfig</filename>"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1438
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kappname; always search for a <filename>.kateconfig</filename> file for "
"local files (not remote files). In addition, it is possible to set options "
"based on wildcards (file extensions) as follows:"
msgstr ""
"&kappname; vedno poiščite datoteko <filename>.kateconfig</filename> za "
"lokalne datoteke (ne oddaljene datoteke). Poleg tega je mogoče nastaviti "
"možnosti, ki temeljijo na nadomestnih znakih (datotečnih končnicah), kot "
"sledi:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: configuring.docbook:1441
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"kate: tab-width 4; indent-width 4; replace-tabs on;\n"
"kate-wildcard(*.xml): indent-width 2;\n"
"kate-wildcard(Makefile): replace-tabs off;"
msgstr ""
"kate: širina zavihka 4; širina zamika 4; zamenjaj zavihke na;\n"
"kate-wildcard(*.xml): širina zamika 2;\n"
"kate-wildcard(Makefile): zamenjava zavihkov izklopljena;"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1443
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this example, all files use a tab-width of 4 spaces, an indent-width of 4 "
"spaces, and tabs are replaced expanded to spaces. However, for all <filename "
"class=\"extension\">*.xml</filename> files, the indent width is set to 2 "
"spaces. And Makefiles use tabs, &ie; tabs are not replaced with spaces."
msgstr ""
"V tem primeru vse datoteke uporabljajo širino zavihka 4 presledke, širino "
"zamika 4 presledke, zavihki pa so zamenjani razširjeni na presledke. Vendar "
"pa je za vse datoteke <filename class=\"extension\">*.xml</filename> širina "
"zamika nastavljena na 2 presledka. In Makefiles uporabljajo zavihke, &ie; "
"zavihki niso nadomeščeni s presledki."

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1448
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Wildcards are semicolon separated, &ie; you can also specify multiple file "
"extensions as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Nadomestni znaki so ločeni s podpičjem, &ie; določite lahko tudi več končnic "
"datotek, kot sledi:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: configuring.docbook:1451
#, no-c-format
msgid "kate-wildcard(*.json;*.xml): indent-width 2;"
msgstr "kate-wildcard(*.json;*.xml): širina zamika 2;"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1453
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Further, you can also use the &MIME; type to match certain files, &eg; to "
"indent all C++ source files with 4 spaces, you can write:"
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega lahko uporabite tudi &MIME; tip za ujemanje z določenimi "
"datotekami, &eg; če želite zamakniti vse izvorne datoteke C++ s 4 presledki, "
"lahko napišete:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: configuring.docbook:1457
#, no-c-format
msgid "kate-mimetype(text/x-c++src): indent-width 4;"
msgstr "kate-mimetype(text/x-c++src): širina zamika 4;"

#. Tag: para
#: configuring.docbook:1459
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Next to the support in <filename>.kateconfig</filename> files, wildcard and "
"&MIME; type dependent document variables are also supported in the files "
"itself as comments."
msgstr ""
"Poleg podpore v datotekah <filename>.kubeconfig</filename>, nadomestni znak "
"in MIME; od tipa odvisne spremenljivke dokumenta so podprte tudi v samih "
"datotekah kot komentarji."

#~ msgid "Show focus frame around editor"
#~ msgstr "Pokaži fokusni okvir okoli urejevalnika"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "When checked the editor shows focus frame around the main source text "
#~ "control."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Ko je označeno, urejevalnik prikaže fokusni okvir okoli glavnega "
#~ "kontrolnika izvornega besedila."
